Class LinkedList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary
      • LinkedList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Enumeration

    public class LinkedList
extends java.util.Dictionary
implements java.util.Enumeration
    This class implements the linked list data structure. This structure was used extensively by KAES, but never by SILKin. It is preserved to maintain compatibility with the original KAES system.
